lead_paragraph: Andy Murray believes the best years of his career could still be  ahead after confirming his status as world number one by beating Novak Djokovic to claim the ATP Tour Finals crown on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: Murray Says His Best Years Can Still Be Ahead of Him
